Service Staff signs in.
Service Staff selects the “Request Swap” button.
System displays the current week schedule.
Service Staff selects the shift that they want to swap.
System displays a list of employees on that shift.
Service Staff selects the person to swap. 
Service Staff submits the requests to the selected employee.
System sends a notification to the selected employee.
Selected employee approves the request.
System sends the confirmation to the staff.
System updates the swap into the schedule.